It's not that I don't have romantic feelings, but when I'm conscious of it, I feel like I'm going to lose, and I've always taken the stance of going out with you on a date... but I'm asking you with an exquisite line whether you're interested in me or not. "Right now, I like 2/3 of my senior. If you let me like 1/3, I'll go out with you." I wanted to cum inside me.
response.tagline: After Enjoying A Date With This Girl Who Isn’t Satisfied With Her Boyfriend We Had An Erotic Kiss And Ended Up With Her Getting A Creampie. Ichika Matsumoto.
